  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>As well as an excellent bedroom product the hotel also boasts a well equipped health and fitness centre equipped with gymnasium, swimming pool, spa, sauna &amp; steam rooms. This is by far the best quality hotel in Stansted - both in terms of the standard of product and the location.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>SurroundingArea</Type>
    <Text>The hotel is just a 2 minute walk via a covered walkway to the main Airport Terminal. This is the only hotel at Stansted Airport linked directly to the Terminal. Exit Junction 8A on the M11.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>RoomTypes</Type>
    <Text>The large rooms are themed in three unique styles - Urban, Ocean and Chilli. All are very contemporary in style and offer views of the airport and runway.Rooms feature much of the latest technology including high speed internet access, LCD Televisions,personal laptop safe and mini bar.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>PropertyInformation</Type>
    <Text>This is a super modern structure, in keeping with the general style of the airport.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>DiningFacilities</Type>
    <Text>The hotel has four individually designed restaurants providing a range of cuisine and both relaxed and elegant dining. The centre piece of the hotel is the spectacular wine tower which houses over 4000 bottles of wine for the true connoisseur.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>Short</Type>
    <Text>The large lobby is one of the key features of the hotel with an atrium which rises to the top floor of the hotel. All of the restaurants are easily accessible directly from the lobby.</Text>
  </Description>
